      "description": "Here's a fantastic opportunity to get behind the wheel of a dependable, well-cared-for vehicle at a great value! This car is in good condition \u2014 it drives smoothly and handles with confidence, giving you that satisfying, reliable ride every time. You'll notice only the minor cosmetic signs of normal everyday use, nothing that takes away from its solid performance and appeal. If you're looking for a trustworthy car without the premium price tag, this one deserves a serious look!",
