    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Solid Value & Ready to Go \u2013 An Honest Fair-Condition Pick! \ud83d\ude97\n\nLooking for a dependable ride that won't break the bank? This vehicle is exactly what it sounds like \u2014 a practical, functional car that gets the job done every day. It shows some normal wear and age, as you'd expect, but it runs well and is ready for the road. No hidden surprises here \u2014 just a straightforward, honest deal for a budget-savvy buyer who wants reliable transportation at a fair price. Come take a look and see for yourself!",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition, and we want to be fully transparent about what you're getting. The exterior shows significant wear \u2014 expect multiple deep scratches, dents, and faded or peeling paint in several areas. The interior is similarly worn, with torn or heavily stained upholstery, damaged trim pieces, and general signs of hard use over the years. Mechanically, the car has known issues that will require attention; it may start and run, but should not be considered reliable without repair work. This listing is best suited for a buyer who is mechanically inclined, looking for a project vehicle, or interested in parts. We are pricing it accordingly and encourage a thorough inspection before purchase \u2014 what you see is what you get.",
      "price": 6000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in fair condition, and we want to give you a complete and honest picture before you make your decision. The exterior shows its age \u2014 expect noticeable scratches, some paint fade, and possibly minor dents or surface blemishes. The body panels are intact with no major structural concerns, but cosmetic imperfections are clearly visible. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it may benefit from some routine maintenance or minor repairs in the near term. The interior is functional but worn \u2014 you'll likely find faded upholstery, some scuffs on trim pieces, and general signs of regular use. All major systems (engine, transmission, brakes, steering) are operational, though we recommend a pre-purchase inspection so you can assess any areas you'd like addressed. This is a solid option for a buyer looking for a dependable, everyday vehicle at a fair price, with the understanding that it is not a showroom-quality car.",
      "price": 15000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed honestly as a good-condition car, making it a reliable choice for buyers seeking dependable used transportation without overpaying for a mint-condition vehicle. The exterior shows only minor surface scratches and light wear consistent with normal daily use \u2014 no major dents, rust, or body damage to report. The interior is clean and functional, with modest wear on high-contact surfaces like the driver's seat and steering wheel, but nothing that detracts from everyday comfort. Mechanically, the car runs well and has been maintained adequately; all major systems \u2014 engine, transmission, brakes, and cooling \u2014 are in good working order. Tires have reasonable tread remaining, and no warning lights are present. This is a solid, honest used car that will serve a buyer well for commuting or family use, with no major surprises expected in the near term.",
      "price": 33000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 34
